<p itemprop="description">A senior business relationship manager leads strategic engagement with key business stakeholders and drives alignment between IT services and business objectives. They mentor junior relationship managers and establish best practices for business engagement.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead strategic relationships with senior business stakeholders</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Develop and execute business engagement strategies</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Mentor and guide junior business relationship managers</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Drive business value realisation from IT investments</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead complex business requirement analysis and solution design</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Establish governance frameworks for business-IT alignment</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support strategic planning and business transformation initiatives</li>
    </ul>
</section>

